<div class="wp-block-group alignfull"><!-- wp:details {"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"margin":{"right":"120px","left":"120px"}}}} -->
<details class="wp-block-details alignfull" style="margin-right:120px;margin-left:120px"><summary>What is CIS Connect, and who is it for?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Type / to add a hidden block"} -->
<p>CIS Connect is a platform that helps Brooklyn College students build a portfolio and find a job in the Computer Science industry.</p>
